{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/happy-birthday/","webpackCompilationHash":"33fb921d112cb791c8ff","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeffry.in","author":"Jeff Wainwright"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bee6aec0-a018-5d1c-822e-d2275aa33026","html":"<p>A year ago I was not able to be with one of my dear friends on their birthday so I made this.</p>\n<p><em>This</em> being posed images of myself to make each letter for the word <em>Happy Birthday</em>.</p>\n<p>I posted the images on Instagram in reverse order so that my friends could slowly get the message that I had <em>posed</em> for them.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/h.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;H&#x27; in Happy birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/a.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;A&#x27; in Happy birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/p.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;P&#x27; in Happy birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/p2.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;P&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/y.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;Y&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/b.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;B&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/i.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;I&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/r.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;R&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/t.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;T&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/h.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;H&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/d.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;D&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/a.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;A&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/y2.jpg\" alt=\"&#x27;Y&#x27; in Happy Birthday\"></p>","frontmatter":{"featured_image":"https://yowainwright.imgix.net/hb/hb.jpg","meta":"A post which creates letters with the body that spell out Happy Birthday!","social_image":null,"title":"Happy Birthday, a project to say happy birthday","date":"May 05, 2014","path":"/happy-birthday/"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false}}}